# StickyDesk runtime data (must never be committed). ANCHORED to repo root with a leading "/"
# so they do NOT also match source folders like StickyDesk.Core/Data — git is case-insensitive
# on Windows, so an unanchored "data/" was excluding the entire Core/Data source tree.
/data/
/attachments/
/logs/
/config/
.portable

